# steps to use:
1- Preferably use virtual env in python for this project.
run: 
  virtualenv .  
  Scripts/activate.bat


2- install libraries specified in the requirements.txt file

3- the order to run the py code is: collect_imgs.py > create_dataset.py > train_classifier.py > inference_classifier.py


+ to use the dataset already existing in this project, run only *inference_classifier.py*